{"id":327,"parent_id":325,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":327,"title":"2 Kings 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Kgs.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","Elisha and the prophets know that Elijah is to be translated—Elijah divides the waters of the Jordan and is taken up into heaven in a whirlwind—The mantle of Elijah falls on Elisha, who also divides the waters of the Jordan—Elisha heals the waters of Jericho—Youths are torn by bears for mocking Elisha."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.1","order":"02.13.002.25903"},["b","1"],"And it came to pass, when the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"would take up Elijah into heaven by a whirlwind, that Elijah went with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Elisha"],"from",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Gilgal"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.2","order":"02.13.002.25904"},["b","2"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Elijah"],"said unto Elisha, Tarry here, I pray thee; for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath sent me to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"Beth-el"],". And Elisha said",["i","unto him, As"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"liveth, and",["i","as"],"thy soul liveth, I will not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"leave"],"thee. So they went down to Beth-el."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.3","order":"02.13.002.25905"},["b","3"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"sons"],"of the prophets that",["i","were"],"at Beth-el came forth to Elisha, and said unto him, Knowest thou that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will take away thy master from thy head to day? And he said, Yea, I know",["i","it;"],"hold ye your peace."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.4","order":"02.13.002.25906"},["b","4"],"And Elijah said unto him, Elisha, tarry here, I pray thee; for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath sent me to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Jericho"],". And he said,",["i","As"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"liveth, and",["i","as"],"thy soul liveth, I will not leave thee. So they came to Jericho."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.5","order":"02.13.002.25907"},["b","5"],"And the sons of the prophets that",["i","were"],"at Jericho came to Elisha, and said unto him, Knowest thou that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will take away thy master from thy head to day? And he answered, Yea, I know",["i","it;"],"hold ye your peace."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.6","order":"02.13.002.25908"},["b","6"],"And Elijah said unto him, Tarry, I pray thee, here; for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath sent me to Jordan. And he said,",["i","As"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"liveth, and",["i","as"],"thy soul liveth, I will not leave thee. And they two went on."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.7","order":"02.13.002.25909"},["b","7"],"And fifty men of the sons of the prophets went, and stood to view afar off: and they two stood by Jordan."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.8","order":"02.13.002.25910"},["b","8"],"And Elijah took his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"mantle"],", and wrapped",["i","it"],"together, and smote the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"waters"],", and they were divided hither and thither, so that they two went over on dry ground."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.9","order":"02.13.002.25911"},["b","9"],"¶And it came to pass, when they were gone over, that Elijah said unto Elisha, Ask what I shall do for thee, before I be taken away from thee. And Elisha said, I pray thee, let a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"double"],"portion of thy spirit be upon me."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.10","order":"02.13.002.25912"},["b","10"],"And he said, Thou hast asked a hard thing:",["i","nevertheless,"],"if thou see me",["i","when I am"],"taken from thee, it shall be so unto thee; but if not, it shall not be",["i","so."]],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.11","order":"02.13.002.25913"},["b","11"],"And it came to pass, as they still went on, and talked, that, behold,",["i","there appeared"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"chariot"],"of fire, and horses of fire, and parted them both asunder; and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"Elijah"],"went up by a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"whirlwind"],"into heaven."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.12","order":"02.13.002.25914"},["b","12"],"¶And Elisha saw",["i","it,"],"and he cried, My father, my father, the chariot of Israel, and the horsemen thereof. And he saw him no more: and he took hold of his own clothes, and rent them in two pieces."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.13","order":"02.13.002.25915"},["b","13"],"He took up also the mantle of Elijah that fell from him, and went back, and stood by the bank of Jordan;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.14","order":"02.13.002.25916"},["b","14"],"And he took the mantle of Elijah that fell from him, and smote the waters, and said, Where",["i","is"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Elijah? and when he also had smitten the waters, they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"parted"],"hither and thither: and Elisha went over."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.15","order":"02.13.002.25917"},["b","15"],"And when the sons of the prophets which",["i","were"],"to view at Jericho saw him, they said, The spirit of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Elijah"],"doth",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"rest"],"on Elisha. And they came to meet him, and bowed themselves to the ground before him."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.16","order":"02.13.002.25918"},["b","16"],"¶And they said unto him, Behold now, there be with thy servants fifty strong men; let them go, we pray thee, and seek thy master: lest peradventure the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Spirit"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath taken him up, and cast him upon some mountain, or into some valley. And he said, Ye shall not send."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.17","order":"02.13.002.25919"},["b","17"],"And when they urged him till he was ashamed, he said, Send. They sent therefore fifty men; and they sought three days, but found him not."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.18","order":"02.13.002.25920"},["b","18"],"And when they came again to him, (for he tarried at Jericho,) he said unto them, Did I not say unto you, Go not?"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.19","order":"02.13.002.25921"},["b","19"],"¶And the men of the city said unto Elisha, Behold, I pray thee, the situation of this city",["i","is"],"pleasant, as my lord seeth: but the water",["i","is"],"naught, and the ground barren."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.20","order":"02.13.002.25922"},["b","20"],"And he said, Bring me a new",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"cruse"],", and put salt therein. And they brought",["i","it"],"to him."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.21","order":"02.13.002.25923"},["b","21"],"And he went forth unto the spring of the waters, and cast the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"salt"],"in there, and said, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", I have healed these",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"waters"],"; there shall not be from thence any more death or",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"barren"],["i","land."]],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.22","order":"02.13.002.25924"},["b","22"],"So the waters were healed unto this day, according to the saying of Elisha which he spake."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.23","order":"02.13.002.25925"},["b","23"],"¶And he went up from thence unto Beth-el: and as he was going up by the way, there came forth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"little children"],"out of the city, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"mocked"],"him, and said unto him, Go up, thou",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"bald"],"head; go up, thou bald head."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.24","order":"02.13.002.25926"},["b","24"],"And he turned back, and looked on them, and cursed them in the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],". And there came forth two she bears out of the wood, and tare forty and two children of them."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.25","order":"02.13.002.25927"},["b","25"],"And he went from thence to mount",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"Carmel"],", and from thence he returned to Samaria."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.1a","order":"02.13.002.25928"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/19.16.16-17"},"1 Kgs. 19:16 (16–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.1b","order":"02.13.002.25930"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/5.9.9-10"},"Josh. 5:9 (9–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/4.38"},"2 Kgs. 4:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.2a","order":"02.13.002.25932"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/25.5.5-6"},"3 Ne. 25:5 (5–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.14.13-16"},"D&C 110:14 (13–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.17.17-18"},"128:17 (17–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.2b","order":"02.13.002.25934"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/12.8.7-8"},"Gen. 12:8 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/28.19.16-19"},"28:19 (16–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/16.2.1-2"},"Josh. 16:2 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.2c","order":"02.13.002.25936"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ruth/1.16.16-17"},"Ruth 1:16 (16–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.3a","order":"02.13.002.25938"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/20.35"},"1 Kgs. 20:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.4a","order":"02.13.002.25940"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/16.34"},"1 Kgs. 16:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.8a","order":"02.13.002.25942"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/19.19"},"1 Kgs. 19:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.8b","order":"02.13.002.25944"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/14.21"},"Ex. 14:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/3.16.14-17"},"Josh. 3:16 (14–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.9a","order":"02.13.002.25946"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/21.17"},"Deut. 21:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.11a","order":"02.13.002.25948"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.7"},"Abr. 2:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.11b","order":"02.13.002.25950"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/translated-beings"},"TG Translated Beings"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.11c","order":"02.13.002.25952"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.4"},"Ezek. 1:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.14a","order":"02.13.002.25954"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/14.21.21-22"},"Ex. 14:21 (21–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.15a","order":"02.13.002.25956"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/2.2.1-3"},"D&C 2:2 (1–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.9"},"27:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.15b","order":"02.13.002.25958"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-ordination"},"TG Priesthood, Ordination"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.16a","order":"02.13.002.25960"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/11.1"},"1 Ne. 11:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/45.19.18-19"},"Alma 45:19 (18–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/6.64"},"Moses 6:64"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.20a","order":"02.13.002.25962"},["b","20a"],["span.small","HEB"],"dish, bowl."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.21a","order":"02.13.002.25964"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/4.41"},"2 Kgs. 4:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.21b","order":"02.13.002.25966"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/15.25"},"Ex. 15:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/47.8.8-9"},"Ezek. 47:8 (8–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.21c","order":"02.13.002.25968"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/barren"},"TG Barren"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.23a","order":"02.13.002.25970"},["b","23a"],["span.small","HEB"],"youths (not little children)."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.23b","order":"02.13.002.25972"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mocking"},"TG Mocking"],"."],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.23c","order":"02.13.002.25974"},["b","23c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.16.16-17"},"Lam. 4:16 (16–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.25a","order":"02.13.002.25976"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/4.25"},"2 Kgs. 4:25"],"."]]}
